file.name: publicity_get.yml
file.content:
Get publicity for owner of current token
---
openapi: 3.0.0
components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT
security:
  - bearerAuth: []
tags:
  - name: User
parameters:
  - name: Authorization
    in: header
    description: "Send like this: Bearer [TOKEN]"
    type: string
    required: true
example:
  Authorization: "Bearer eyJ0eXAiOi...."
responses:
  200:
    description: "Return publicity"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        publicity:
          type: boolean 
          description: User's publicity
      publicity:
        msg: true
